<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-1">Accessibility</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Braille translation service<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled WC<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Induction loop<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Text Relay<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Signing service available<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Wheelchair access<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Step free access<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent3a46f03e932b49d8b4d0c935a2fb1dae">
</div>
<p>There is easy disabled access at the Trelawny Wing and Tower Block entrances.</p>
