<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-5">Faith services</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Prayer area<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">On-site chapel<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContentfdd3ffd8e5364f3bbfb824011a1616ba">
</div>
<p>The hospital's pastoral and spirtual care team provides a multi-faith service for patients. The team has links with spiritual representatives from a wide range of faiths in the community and can arrange visits. The team can be contacted on 01872 252883.</p>
